<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id52703746-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6" identifier="/us/usc/t28/s538"><num value="538">§ 538.</num><heading> Investigation of aircraft piracy and related violations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Federal Bureau of Investigation shall investigate any violation of section 46314 or chapter 465 of title 49.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id52703747-3a70-11f1-9e0c-dcbb1364dae6">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s4/e/1">Pub. L. 103–272, § 4(e)(1)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1361">108 Stat. 1361</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
